Frequently-used unicode for quantum notation


https://github.com/j6k4m8/espanso-quantum

| Abbreviation | Expansion |
|--------------|-----------|
|<kbd>\\\\to</kbd> | → |
|<kbd>\\\\bn</kbd> | ℕ |
|<kbd>\\\\br</kbd> | ℝ |
|<kbd>\\\\pi</kbd> | π |
|<kbd>\\\\bb</kbd> | 𝔹 |
|<kbd>\\\\cdot</kbd> | ⋅ |
|<kbd>\\\\theta</kbd> | θ |
|<kbd>\\\\psi</kbd> | ψ |
|<kbd>\\\\lambda</kbd> | λ |
|<kbd>\\\\neg</kbd> | ¬ |
|<kbd>\\\\times</kbd> | × |
|<kbd>\\\\pm</kbd> | ± |
|<kbd>\\\\b1</kbd> | 𝟙 |
|<kbd>\\\\bra</kbd> | ⟨ |
|<kbd>\\\\ket</kbd> | ⟩ |
